channel.title: Four Questions
channel.description:
Ookay, Four easy questions (Very Noobish, Yes, But I forgot how to do it :o )
1) How do I make Places Safe Zones, Or A Non Safe Zone
[s]2) How do I make a door open or close when you click on it (I added this in object.cfg: [/s] [s]3) How do I change the max amount of money ( Did it once, and forgot :o )[/s]
4) Im Using Satan's Isle, (Re-doing it pretty much completely) And you can't teleport, I was wondering if there was a way i could fix this.
Any Help at all is Appreciated
Thanks
